When I started to navigate my way around the app, I got a notification saying a virus was on my phone. I was super tired at this point so I just went to sleep and hoped the virus was fake or that it would go away. In the morning, I couldnâ€™t open my phone anymore. It would let turn on. I had to call Apple to help me fix it. I ended up having to pay $1,100 for a new phone. I think I will sue you guys.
